        <Parent_String>knives for serving food [300207611], culinary knives [300266867], knives [300024668], cutting tools [300024662], cutting equipment [300163290], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
